cs.DL, cs.IR, cs.SI, cs.CY, cs.CR 

The paper analyzes the presence and possibilities of altmetrics for bibliometric and performance analysis across fields and document types. This suggests that it could fit into several arXiv CS sub-categories, including digital libraries (cs.DL), information retrieval (cs.IR), social and information networks (cs.SI), computers and society (cs.CY), and cryptography and security (cs.CR). However, given the focus on bibliometrics and publication analysis, cs.DL and cs.IR are the most likely categories.
